updateStatus

protected void updateStatus(long rcvrStatus)
                     throws ScriptingException
This is a protected function called from CToolsTraceChannel.getStatus() to update m_status member variable value. This value is gotten from native function call and trace status do not have communication channel with native function. Thus, the status value needed to be update via external source.

Throws:
ScriptingException
